<p>The 2020 VMA tribute video, which was presented by Blink 182's Travis Barker, also paid homage to other fallen stars in the music world from the past year.</p>

<p>Glee star Naya Rivera, who tragically died in a boating accident in Southern California this summer at the age of 33, was also included.  </p>

<p>Others included Juice WRLD, who died of an overdose late last year at the young age of 21. </p>

